{"word":"G4800 - συζάω - syzáō - sood-zah'-o - Live with","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συζάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">syzáō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">sood-zah'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Live with</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கூடப்பிழை"},{"paragraph":"to live together with"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G2198 - ζάω - záō - dzah'-o/2198\">G2198</a>; to continue to <i>live</i> in common <i>with</i>, that is, <i>co-survive</i> (literally or figuratively): - live with.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4776/4776\">G4776</a>, <a href=\"#/G4789/4789\">G4789</a>, <a href=\"#/G4800/4800\">G4800</a>, <a href=\"#/G4806/4806\">G4806</a>, <a href=\"#/G4821/4821\">G4821</a>, <a href=\"#/G4832/4832\">G4832</a>, <a href=\"#/G4833/4833\">G4833</a>, <a href=\"#/G4841/4841\">G4841</a>, <a href=\"#/G4854/4854\">G4854</a>, <a href=\"#/G4855/4855\">G4855</a>, <a href=\"#/G4862/4862\">G4862</a>, <a href=\"#/G4880/4880\">G4880</a>, <a href=\"#/G4888/4888\">G4888</a>, <a href=\"#/G4891/4891\">G4891</a>, <a href=\"#/G4916/4916\">G4916</a>, <a href=\"#/G4957/4957\">G4957</a>"}]}